      "title": "Petrol ship to Colombo tonight",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that a ship carrying a cargo of 35,000 metric tons of petrol is scheduled to arrive in Colombo tonight (18th).",
        "It is further reported that after the completion of the inspection of the petrol stock, the unloading will begin and after that the distribution will begin as soon as possible."
      ],
